Also Download Metadata table for Attribute Definition: http://gis.drcog.org/datacatalog/node/303    The following census tables are available in this .csv file: B08013 - AGGREGATE TRAVEL TIME TO WORK (IN MINUTES) OF WORKERS BY SEX B08101 - MEANS OF TRANSPORTATION TO WORK BY AGE B08201 - HOUSEHOLD SIZE BY VEHICLES AVAILABLE B08202 - HOUSEHOLD SIZE BY NUMBER OF WORKERS IN HOUSEHOLD B17001 - POVERTY STATUS IN THE PAST 12 MONTHS BY SEX BY AGE B19080 - HOUSEHOLD INCOME QUINTILE UPPER LIMITS B19081 - MEAN HOUSEHOLD INCOME OF QUINTILES B19082 - SHARES OF AGGREGATE HOUSEHOLD INCOME BY QUINTILE B19101 - FAMILY INCOME IN THE PAST 12 MONTHS (IN 2010 INFLATION-ADJUSTED DOLLARS)   The ACS data by Place can be linked using the GEOID10 field, to the GEOID10 field in the TRACTS_2010 Dataset: http://gis.drcog.org/datacatalog/content/tracts-census-2010        NOTE: When importing the .csv files into a Database, the software may try to turn the geoid field into a number field, which will drop the first 0 from the census code and will make the table not linkable to the geographies. Whatever software you import the table with, you will want to make sure that field gets imported as a string or text field.</dct:description>     <foaf:homepage rdf:resource="http://data.opencolorado.org/dataset/drcog-2012-acs-5-year-survey-tract-level-data-colorado-table-1"></foaf:homepage>     <rdfs:label>drcog-2012-acs-5-year-survey-tract-level-data-colorado-table-1</rdfs:label>     <dct:identifier>drcog-2012-acs-5-year-survey-tract-level-data-colorado-table-1</dct:identifier>     <dct:title>DRCOG:           2012 ACS 5 Year Survey - Tract Level Data, Colorado (Table 1)        </dct:title>         <dcat:distribution>             <dcat:Distribution>                 <dcat:accessURL rdf:resource="http://gis.drcog.org/datacatalog/sites/default/files/TRACT_ACS_5YR_2012.csv"></dcat:accessURL>                     <dct:format>                         <dct:IMT>                             <rdf:value>CSV</rdf:value>                             <rdfs:label>CSV</rdfs:label>                         </dct:IMT>                     </dct:format>                <dct:title>TRACT_ACS_5YR_2012.csv</dct:title>             </dcat:Distribution>         </dcat:distribution>     <dct:creator>       <rdf:Description>         <foaf:name>DRCOG</foaf:name>         <foaf:mbox rdf:resource="mailto:"></foaf:mbox>       </rdf:Description>     </dct:creator>     <dct:contributor>       <rdf:Description>         <foaf:name>DRCOG Geospatial Team</foaf:name>         <foaf:mbox rdf:resource="mailto:geospatial@drcog.org"></foaf:mbox>       </rdf:Description>     </dct:contributor>     <dct:rights rdf:resource="http://www.opendefinition.org/licenses/cc-by"></dct:rights>   </dcat:Dataset> </rdf:RDF>
